headline: DHF: Don't Be Misled By The Strong Recent Performance

headline: Constellation Energy Agrees to Buy Calpine for $16.4 Billion
summary: Constellation Energy  agreed to buy Calpine for $16.4 billion, combining two of the country’s largest electricity generators at a time when their product is in high demand from tech companies.  Including the assumption of debt, Constellation on Friday valued the cash-and-stock deal for the privately held Calpine at $26.6 billion.  The value of power generators has soared in the past year due in large part to artificial intelligence.
